    "description": "Grow your career with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd! We are hiring a Front Office Manager for our Nagpur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd:\nMcDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Plan and execute banquets, events, and MICE functions\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Conduct regular guest satisfaction surveys and implement improvements\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n• Train and supervise front-line staff on service standards\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• CA / CMA / CFA certification\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in Crisis Management\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with McDonald's India Consulting Pvt Ltd!",
